<p><b>Is 7 out of 9 a good score in IELTS?</b> Each of the four sections will be scored on a scale of 1 to 9, and in addition to that, you will receive an overall band score. A “good” IELTS band score is 7.0 or higher. A band 7.0 is defined as a “good user“, a band 8.0 a “very good user“, and a 9.0 an “expert” user.</p>
